languages.text: "Приятно иметь дело с тем, кто знает, чего хочет. Грамоту я заберу себе, вы же не против? Ну а в комнатке позади для вас тоже кое-что есть".

traits.locale_text: "Приятно иметь дело с тем, кто знает, чего хочет. Грамоту я заберу себе, вы же не против? Ну а в комнатке позади для вас тоже кое-что есть".

languages.text: "It's nice to do business with somebody who knows what they want. I'll take the certificate, if you don't mind? And there's something for you too in the room behind you."

languages.text: 「何が欲しいのがか分かっている方とのビジネスは良いものですね。もしよろしければ、証明書をお預かりしましょうか？それから、あなたの後ろの部屋にもいいものがありますよ」
languages.original_text: "It's nice to do business with somebody who knows what they want. I'll take the certificate, if you don't mind? And there's something for you too in the room behind you."

languages.text: “和知道想要什么的人做生意就是痛快。那我就把执照拿走了，你不会介意吧？对了，你身后的房间里，有我为你准备的礼物。”
languages.original_text: "It's nice to do business with somebody who knows what they want. I'll take the certificate, if you don't mind? And there's something for you too in the room behind you."

traits.locale_text: “和知道想要什么的人做生意就是痛快。那我就把执照拿走了，你不会介意吧？对了，你身后的房间里，有我为你准备的礼物。”

languages.text: «Se agradece tratar con alguien que tiene las cosas claras. Si me disculpa, me llevo el certificado. Por cierto, en la sala que tiene detrás, hay algo para usted también».
languages.original_text: "It's nice to do business with somebody who knows what they want. I'll take the certificate, if you don't mind? And there's something for you too in the room behind you."

languages.text: « C'est agréable de faire affaire avec quelqu'un qui sait ce qu'il veut. Je vais vous débarrasser du certificat, si cela ne vous dérange pas. Et il y a quelque chose qui vous attend dans la pièce derrière vous. »
languages.original_text: "It's nice to do business with somebody who knows what they want. I'll take the certificate, if you don't mind? And there's something for you too in the room behind you."

languages.text: "Es ist schön, mit jemandem Geschäfte zu machen, der weiß, was er will. Ich nehme dann das Zertifikat, falls Ihr nichts dagegen habt? In dem Raum hinter Euch wartet schon etwas auf Euch."
languages.original_text: "It's nice to do business with somebody who knows what they want. I'll take the certificate, if you don't mind? And there's something for you too in the room behind you."

languages.text: "Ne istediğini bilen biriyle iş yapmak ne güzel. Mahsuru yoksa tasdiknameyi alabilir miyim? Senin alacağın da arkandaki odada."
languages.original_text: "It's nice to do business with somebody who knows what they want. I'll take the certificate, if you don't mind? And there's something for you too in the room behind you."

traits.locale_text: "Ne istediğini bilen biriyle iş yapınca güzel oluyor. Mahsuru yoksa tasdiknameyi alabilir miyim? Arkandaki odada da sana bir şey var."
